{"_path":"/city/t022","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"報稅 - 扣除額","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t022-1.jpeg","sequence":22,"category":"年度報稅","author":"財政部","link":"https://www.facebook.com/mof.gov.tw/posts/pfbid0mypikqy3B92CXD7Nymk1ZVP8EwmKzz7Be8rogDhHNcdaWMRCoC28F3haQ2oMRvznl","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-04-15T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"扣除額"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"扣除額"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"一般扣除額"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一般扣除額"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今年 5 月 #綜所稅申報，除了特別扣除額外，還有一般扣除額可以扣除，又分為大家常聽到的「標準扣除額」及「列舉扣除額」2 選 1，哪個對自己更有利就選哪個！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"✎#標準扣除額：單身者享 12.4 萬元，與配偶合併申報者加倍 24.8 萬元，申報時直接扣除，免附證明文件。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✎#列舉扣除額：6 項包含捐贈、保險費、醫藥及生育費、災害損失、購屋借款利息、房屋租金支出，申報時須附證明文件，但依稽徵機關提供查詢的資料申報可以免附（購屋借款利息除外）。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n記住一個重點：若可列舉扣除的金額合計超過標準扣除額，就採逐一列舉比較划算！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t022-2.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t022-2.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t022-3.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t022-3.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t022-4.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t022-4.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t022-5.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t022-5.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t022-6.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t022-6.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"特別扣除額"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"特別扣除額"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今年 5 月 #綜所稅申報，大家最關心的就是有多少扣除額可以減稅啦！一起來複習 7 項特別扣除額，符合條件即可適用。另外也提醒大家："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✎ 薪資所得、儲蓄投資、幼兒學前：申報時直接扣除，免附證明文件。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✎ 身心障礙、長期照顧、財產交易損失、教育學費：須附證明文件，但如果依稽徵機關提供查詢的資料申報，可以免附。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"📍 檢附文件這裡看："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://gov.tw/8oZ","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://gov.tw/8oZ"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n☎ 稅務諮詢專線：0800-000-321（市話） （或逕洽戶籍地國稅局由專人為您解說）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t022-1.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t022-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"扣除額","depth":2,"text":"扣除額","children":[{"id":"一般扣除額","depth":3,"text":"一般扣除額"},{"id":"特別扣除額","depth":3,"text":"特別扣除額"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:city:t022.md","_source":"content","_file":"city/t022.md","_extension":"md"}